9.text: Ɛtoɔ tua ho nhyehyԑeԑ sesa wɔ aman ahodoɔ so, ԑnna ԑtoɔ dodoɔ a obi tua ԑne nnipa a wɔtua toɔ no sesa wɔ aman foforɔ so.

0.text: Ɛda a wɔbԑfrԑ asԑm no nso yԑ da a ԑwɔ hɔ ma deԑ wɔabɔ no kwaadu no sԑ wɔbԑdi n’asԑm no ntԑntԑm.

1.text: Ɛnnԑ anɔpa pa ara no, na mframa yԑ ‘83 km/h’ na ani da so sԑ ԑso bԑkɔ so ate.

2.text: Akwaa no mu deԑ ԑhia pa ara ‘aforo sane die wɔ nnipadua’ no mu ne akoma, ԑno na ԑpu mogya gu nnipadua no mu.

3.text: Nkrɔfo pii kɔ saa wɛbsaet ahorow yi hɔ, ne titirw adesuafo.

4.text: Nnipakuo nsrahwɛ boɔ yɛ fo, eno nti sɛ ɛyɛ wo nkoaa anaa wo ne adamfo bi no, bɔ mmɔden hyia afoforɔ na monhyehyɛ ekuo a nnipa bɛyɛ anan kosi nsia wo mu na ama ɔbaakofoɔ boɔ ayɛ deɛ ɛwɔ fam.

5.text: Medium-format sini ho mfonintwa mfidie de 6 by 6 cm yɛbea na ɛyɛ adwuma, te sɛ 56 by 56 mm negative pɛpɛɛpɛ.

6.text: Yɛ na fa wo amansɛm ho nsɛsoɔ ne nipa a ɔyɛ nsiakyibaa no ɔfrɛ ho nsɛm ka wo ho.
